public class ReaderExplorerView
extends org.eclipse.ui.part.ViewPart

The Reader Management View. It embeds one TreeViewer, and illustrates the Adapter/Reader relationship in tree-like hierarchy. Only two partitions are defined, XML tag and XML comment.
